snippet.title: The Sinking City | PlayStation®5 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sinking City is coming to PlayStation®5 on February 19th, 2021! Play this Lovecraftian detective adventure in glorious 4K/60FPS, with instantaneous loading times, DualSense features and more! 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Tortured by his past and otherworldly visions, private investigator Charles W. Reed finds himself in Oakmont, Massachusetts, seeking salvation from the creeping insanity that afflicts him. 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
For more updates follow The Sinking City on:
• FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/TheSinkingCityGame
• TWITTER: https://twitter.com/thesinkingcity
